## Order templates

The general templates related to orders are

- **Orders:** This is the front-end order management page. It requires **Orders (VX)** widget
- **Cart Summary:** Shows a summary of your order before proceeding to **Checkout**. This page requires **Cart Summary (VX)** widget
- **Stripe Connect account:** Vendor onboarding page, needed if you are creating a marketplace. Requires **Stripe Connect (VX)** widget.
